// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1659 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 1656a078-5049-5d83-a136-d63eb3b765d5

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.04*")
